name: Wedding invitations - Dandelion
description:
Flat style dandelion wedding invitation.

:: Dandelion design in fern green
:: Digitally printed with pigment inks 
:: Natural white luxury 300gsm card 
:: Card measures 145 x 145mm 
:: Kraft brown 100% recycled envelope 
:: Card 50% recycled

ORDERING PROCESS 
If you'd like to place an order for customised wedding stationery in this design and colour scheme:

1. Please add the quantity required to cart (minimum qty of 10)
2. Use the 'Contact us' form on this website to send me the details you would like on these invitations. 
3. I will email you a proof with your details (usually within 2-3 days). 
4. Once any amends have been done and you're happy, your stationery will be printed and delivered (please allow 2 - 3 weeks).

Matching RSVPs, information cards, table numbers, menus, name cards, Order of Service, thank you cards etc. also available.

SAMPLES 
I recommend that you purchase a sample before ordering custom stationery to ensure the colours match your colour scheme. 

To purchase a sample please just 'add to cart' qty of one of this listing.

Sorry samples cannot be customised with your wedding details.

POSTAGE 
Flat rate delivery of £1.00 no matter how many items you order - UK only

Please visit www.gooseberrymoon.co.uk for full range
